## 4. ⚠️ CRITICAL: Unicode Encoding Rules
 
**The data file MUST be pure ASCII.** No raw emoji or special characters are allowed — they cause garbled rendering when written on Windows systems.
 
**Always use JavaScript Unicode escape sequences inside string literals:**
 
| Character | Escape | Usage |
|-----------|--------|-------|
| → | `\u2192` | arrows, "View all →" |
| — | `\u2014` | em dash in titles and descriptions |
| – | `\u2013` | en dash in ranges ("10 PM – late") |
| · | `\u00B7` | separator in trip meta fields |
| ♡ | `\u2661` | Save button heart |
| ✕ | `\u2715` | Modal close button |
| 🇸🇬 | `\uD83C\uDDF8\uD83C\uDDEC` | Singapore flag |
| 🚤 | `\uD83D\uDEA4` | ferry transport |
| 🚗 | `\uD83D\uDE97` | car/drive transport |
| ✈️ | `\u2708\uFE0F` | plane transport |
| 📍 | `\uD83D\uDCCD` | location pin |
| 💵 | `\uD83D\uDCB5` | price/money |
| ⏱ | `\u23F1` | duration/time |
| 📅 | `\uD83D\uDCC5` | calendar date |
| 🕐 | `\uD83D\uDD50` | clock/time |
| 🏋️ | `\uD83C\uDFCB\uFE0F` | sports/gym |
| 🍸 | `\uD83C\uDF78` | nightlife/cocktail |
| 🍜 | `\uD83C\uDF5C` | food |
| 🌿 | `\uD83C\uDF3F` | nature |
| 🎨 | `\uD83C\uDFA8` | culture/art |
| 🤝 | `\uD83E\uDD1D` | community/social |
| ✦ | `\u2726` | sparkle (used in "All" category icon) |
| 🤖 | `\uD83E\uDD16` | robot (AI agent badge) |
| 🏃 | `\uD83C\uDFC3` | running |
| 🎵 | `\uD83C\uDFB5` | music |
 
**In JSX**, wrap escapes in curly braces: `{'\u2192'}` or `{'\uD83D\uDEA4'}`
**In JS string values** (inside data objects), use them directly: `'transport \u2014 description'`
 
